Reasoning: 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is the most likely category as the paper discusses security solutions for embedded processors. 
- cs.EM (Electromagnetics) is also likely as the paper uses multi-band radio frequency measurements to make inferences about program execution. 
- cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) is another possibility as the paper discusses the limitations of dedicated embedded processors and proposes a solution using out-of-band measurements. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a potential category as the paper models program execution using control flow graphs and transitions between nodes. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also possible as the paper discusses program modifications to improve tracking performance.
